dehomopolymerate
------------------------------------------
Collapse sequence homopolymers to a single character

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  zlib0-1.3.2-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  make-4.4.1-2
  zlib-devel-1.3.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/tseemann/dehomopolymerate

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/tseemann/dehomopolymerate/archive/refs/tags/v0.4.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack dehomopolymerate-0.4.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./dehomopolymerate-0.4.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/dehomopolymerate-0.4.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/dehomopolymerate-0.4.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(dehomopolymerate)
  /usr/bin/dehomopolymerate.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/dehomopolymerate.README
  /usr/share/doc/dehomopolymerate/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/dehomopolymerate/README.md

------------------

